  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> You experience the surreal nightmare of an insect. A squirrel tries to fly. An alligator is going through an existential crisis. A bridge made of flesh is broken. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This bridge eats squirrel’s parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.poster.avif?t=1728940521\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.webm?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.mp4?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This surreal universe can turn out disturbingly relatable. It’s a dark existential experience that can be interpreted in many ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.poster.avif?t=1728940521\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.webm?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.mp4?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a praying mantis, you explore an eerie world, meet animals, collect dreams, and make impactful decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Playtime of about 1h</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Exploration game with casual mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interactive story with 2 different endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Disturbing, violent, and poetic story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Meet depressing squirrels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play as a praying mantis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What players say : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“it's so aesthetically and tonally unsettling”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“When the credits roll you will be thinking about the game, and yourself, and if you should have done it differently”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“It's a unique, creative, and well done dive into a mind in crisis”</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br> You experience the surreal nightmare of an insect. A squirrel tries to fly. An alligator is going through an existential crisis. A bridge made of flesh is broken. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This bridge eats squirrel’s parts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.poster.avif?t=1728940521\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.webm?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/e37d6977d2723c626d1b9c478a6a92de.mp4?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This surreal universe can turn out disturbingly relatable. It’s a dark existential experience that can be interpreted in many ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.poster.avif?t=1728940521\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.webm?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1681480/extras/cd15acbdc16aedf42316171e6d929aa6.mp4?t=1728940521\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a praying mantis, you explore an eerie world, meet animals, collect dreams, and make impactful decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Playtime of about 1h</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Exploration game with casual mechanics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Interactive story with 2 different endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Disturbing, violent, and poetic story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Meet depressing squirrels</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Play as a praying mantis</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >What players say : </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“it's so aesthetically and tonally unsettling”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“When the credits roll you will be thinking about the game, and yourself, and if you should have done it differently”</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- <i>“It's a unique, creative, and well done dive into a mind in crisis”</i></p>",
